r: #ccc;">say all the law firms</a> that work with special purpose investme=
nt companies:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">When 49 major nat=
ional law firms banded together late last week to=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://l=
ink.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24898515.251678/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucm9wZX=
NncmF5LmNvbS9lbi9uZXdzcm9vbS9hbGVydHMvMjAyMS9BdWd1c3QvNDktb2YtdGhlLU5hdGlvb=
nMtTGVhZGluZy1MYXctRmlybXMtUmVzcG9uZC10by1JbnZlc3RtZW50LUNvbXBhbnktQWN0LUxh=
